title: Quarter-Season NFL Awards with Brady Quinn (Football 10/2)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to hand out quarter-season awards and superlatives. Superlatives/awards include: Best Backup QB (5:45), Best 2nd-Year QB (10:40), Worst Rookie Head Coach (15:05), Biggest Problem in the League (26:30), Most Entertain Team (other than the Chiefs (30:30), Best Defense (33:10), Offensive Rookie of the Year (38:30), Defensive Rookie of the Year (41:45), Coach of the Year (46:15), Defensive Player of the Year (48:15), and finally MVP (51:45).
